raw_data.education_and_experience_substitution: Education: An Associate’s degree will equal two (2) years of experience. A Bachelor’s degree will equal four (4) years of experience. A Master’s Degree will equal six (6) years of experience. A Doctorate will equal eight (8) years of experience.  Experience: For every year of applicable experience, the person shall be credited with one year of degree qualifications toward the values stated in the labor category descriptions.

raw_data.title: Administrative
